description.en: Pocket Studio: Sing SOMESING for Free ! SOMESING's online Karaoke Platform allows anyone to sing for free, users can receive rewards through the tokens accumulated in the song content by support and gift. SOMESING released its official version on November 19, 2019. Our service is settling well at the beginning. Within 24 hours of launch, approximately 20K transactions and 1K song content were posted in the app, with a DAU of 6K.
